patthana16.7:1.1_0: Abyākato appaccayo dhammo naabyākatassa naappaccayassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo.
patthana16.7:1.1_1: Abyākato appaccayo dhammo nakusalassa naappaccayassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo.
patthana16.7:1.1_2: Abyākato appaccayo dhammo naakusalassa naappaccayassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo.
patthana16.7:1.1_3: Abyākato appaccayo dhammo naakusalassa naappaccayassa ca naabyākatassa naappaccayassa ca dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo.
patthana16.7:1.1_4: Abyākato appaccayo dhammo nakusalassa naappaccayassa ca naakusalassa naappaccayassa ca dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo.
